    "Other short hand included i/b for \"inboard\", o/b for \"outboard\", a/c for \"aircraft\", cht for \"cylinder head temperature\", egt for \"exhaust gas temperature\", c/w for \"complied with\", fdm for \"flight data monitoring\", and many more.",
    "We tried to be as exhaustive as possible in the task of replacing abbreviations with the full words and phrases.",
    "In the next step, we focus on eliminating stop words.",
    "We know that stop words can either be a nuisance or of great value in technical text.",
    "So, we need to ensure that the stop words we choose to remove are appropriate in the context of the MWOs."
